---
const founders = [
  {
    initial: 'A',
    name: 'Alex',
    role: 'Operations & Strategy',
  },
  {
    initial: 'A',
    name: 'Ana',
    role: 'Systems & Implementation',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-brand-bg">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

      <!-- Left: Authority text -->
      <div>
        <p class="section-label mb-6">Why Us</p>
        <h2 class="font-poppins font-bold text-3xl md:text-5xl text-brand-text leading-tight mb-8">
          We've been inside businesses like yours.<br class="hidden md:block" />
          We know what's breaking it.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-5 font-inter text-base text-brand-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">
          <p>
            Between us, we have 30+ years running and operating project-based
            businesses — construction, services, trades. We've felt the pressure,
            missed the numbers, chased the invoices.
          </p>
          <p>
            Then we spent years learning how AI and automation actually work in
            the real world — not in a pitch deck, but on the floor, with real
            teams, real resistance, real change.
          </p>
          <p>
            That combination is rare. Most tech companies don't understand your
            business. Most consultants don't understand the technology. We do both.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pull quote -->
        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-brand-accent pl-6">
          <p class="font-poppins font-medium text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-text leading-snug">
            "We're not here to sell you software. We're here to fix the part of
            your business that's been costing you quietly for years."
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Founder cards -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 lg:pt-16">
        {founders.map((founder) => (
          <div class="bg-brand-surface rounded-2xl p-7 flex items-center gap-6">
            <!-- Avatar placeholder -->
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-brand-accent flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
            >
              <span class="font-poppins font-semibold text-xl text-white">
                {founder.initial}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-poppins font-semibold text-lg text-brand-text mb-1">
                {founder.name}
              </p>
              <p class="font-inter text-sm text-brand-muted">
                {founder.role}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}

        <!-- Stat block -->
        <div class="bg-brand-surface rounded-2xl p-7 mt-2">
          <p class="font-poppins font-bold text-4xl text-brand-accent mb-2">30+</p>
          <p class="font-inter text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">
            Years of combined operational experience across project-based
            businesses, now applied through AI.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
